作用 blocks 可用于
  1. to implement callbacks 
  2. to pass around chunks of code
  3. to implement iterators.
        例:  animals = %w( ant bee cat dog )
             # create an array
             animals.each {|animal| puts animal }

形式1
{ puts "hello"}

形式2
do
  club.enroll(person)
  person.socialize
end

带参数
def who_says_what
  yield("Dave", "hello")
  yield("Andy", "goodbye")
end
who_says_what {|person, phrase| puts "#{person} says #{phrase}"}

两种形式区别 the braces bind more tightly than the do / end pairs
braces for single-line blocks and do / end for multiline blocks
